  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Grease a 9x13 inch baking dish with olive oil.",
    "In a large pan, heat the olive oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for another minute.",
    "Stir in the tomato paste, cumin, and paprika. Cook for 1-2 minutes.",
    "Add the chickpeas, lemon juice, salt, and chopped parsley. Stir to combine.",
    "Transfer the mixture to the prepared baking dish.",
    "Bake for 25-30 minutes or until the top is lightly browned.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
